<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
    color: #333;
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
}

.navbar {
    background: #ffffff;
    box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}

.navbar-brand {
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #333 !important;
}

.nav-link {
    color: #555 !important;
    transition: color 0.3s ease-in-out;
}

.nav-link:hover {
    color: #007bff !important;
}

.hero-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #007bff, #00c6ff);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
}

.hero-section h1 {
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
}

.hero-section p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
}

.btn-primary {
    background-color: #007bff;
    border: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
}

.btn-primary:hover {
    background-color: #0056b3;
}

.card {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
}

.card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
}

.card-title {
    color: #007bff;
    font-weight: bold;
}

.why-choose {
    background: #ffffff;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}

.why-choose h2 {
    color: #007bff;
    font-weight: bold;
}

.why-choose h5 {
    color: #333;
}

.why-choose p {
    color: #666;
}

footer {
    background: #333;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 2rem 0;
    text-align: center;
}

footer a {
    color: #00c6ff;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.3s ease-in-out;
}

footer a:hover {
    color: #007bff;
}

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%-include("NavBar")%>
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="hero-section">
            <h1>Welcome to MyBlog</h1>
            <p>Your go-to platform for exciting blogs and articles.</p>
            <a href="/signup" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
        </div>

        <div class="row mt-5">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="/uploads/img1.jpg" class="card-img-top img-fluid" alt="Blog 1">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Blog Title 1</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Vivamus lacinia odio vitae vestibulum.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Read More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="/uploads/img2.jpg" class="card-img-top img-fluid" alt="Blog 2">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Blog Title 2</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Vivamus lacinia odio vitae vestibulum.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Read More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="/uploads/img3.jpg" class="card-img-top img-fluid" alt="Blog 3">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Blog Title 3</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Vivamus lacinia odio vitae vestibulum.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Read More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="why-choose">
            <h2 class="text-center">Why Choose MyBlog?</h2>
            <p class="text-center">We provide insightful articles and engaging content on a variety of topics to keep you informed and entertained.</p>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <h5>Wide Variety of Topics</h5>
                    <p>Explore articles ranging from technology to lifestyle, ensuring there's something for everyone.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <h5>Expert Writers</h5>
                    <p>Our content is created by experienced writers to ensure quality and reliability.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <h5>Community Driven</h5>
                    <p>Join our vibrant community of readers and share your thoughts through comments and feedback.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2024 MyBlog. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>Follow us on:
                <a href="#" class="text-decoration-none">Facebook</a>,
                <a href="#" class="text-decoration-none">Twitter</a>,
                <a href="#" class="text-decoration-none">Instagram</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
